Package helper

Class Excel

java.lang.Object
helper.Excel
public class Excel extends Object
A helper class that can read in and store details about the model classes Student, Faculty, FYPCoordinator, Project and Request from data files. It can also write the updated information from these classes into the data files.
Since:
2023-04-13
Version:
1.0
